{"tid":472801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府一路逼後生高價買樓，然後用地價收入維穩瘋狂打壓年輕人","createTime":"2017-11-18T14:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T01:50:31.000Z","uid":33307,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a9e2622fc6c9a784737a832e26e07fcea61867b8","tid":472801,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:40:10.000Z","msg":"日日宣傳冇樓就係廢青<br />\n逼人高價買樓，否則結婚生仔都唔得<br />\n跟住用高價賣地收益維穩<br />\n逼OT錢警察清場<br />\n大規模搞國教<br />\n出錢比打手入場唱國歌<br />\n搞支那交流團/普教中<br />\n<br />\n點解年輕人鬥唔過政府？<br />\n因為佢地供緊錢比政府對付自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ed57bb0435c745d6a3b2a34d1923d8cc532629","tid":472801,"uid":102198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:41:21.000Z","msg":"駁吾刀"},{"pid":"087859128da13b644d62fad2419f2a1e12a39c09","tid":472801,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今次咁正常"},{"pid":"888d383b37af4bcb0a3445a84d90084847405b54","tid":472801,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T15:04:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今次咁正常</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b09a80e0eb9b4626012a76ec338bc064876b543","tid":472801,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T17:20:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>駁吾刀</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a334a2247e309ebdacab85ab29b04efb239fec7d","tid":472801,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,